    "description": "在这款逼真的轰炸机模拟游戏中操控一架B-17，炮轰敌军的关键目标。<br>控制飞行中队的每个成员，感受命悬一线的时刻。在被纳粹德国占领的欧洲大陆加入历史性的伟大战役。<br><br>主要特色：<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>管理B-17中队。<br></li><li>直接控制中队的每位成员。<br></li><li>摧毁目标。<br></li><li>与敌军飞机作战。<br></li><li>指挥整个中队。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/8266648c3688fc2d6d501c8325b1e659.poster.avif?t=1767865416\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/8266648c3688fc2d6d501c8325b1e659.webm?t=1767865416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>强悍的轰炸机、骁勇的飞行员</strong><br>你的轰炸机全副武装，载有数吨货物。<br>然而即使是最精良的装备，如果没了骁勇善战的飞行员，也无法对敌人构成威胁。<br>你将作为机长或副驾驶员操控B-17，对飞行参数、发动机转速、襟翼等进行操控。<br>在无线电站，你还能接发报告、研究地图、帮助中队抵达目标。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/0d4eb522f658e58d736742fba400d188.poster.avif?t=1767865416\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/0d4eb522f658e58d736742fba400d188.webm?t=1767865416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>返航。</strong><br>已经扔下炸弹，摧毁了敌军目标？<br>但你的任务还未完成。为了作为指挥官参加下一次任务，你需要带领中队成功返航。如果轰炸机受损，沿途将遇到巨大挑战。<br>看着轰炸机被敌军击中，体验生死攸关的分分秒秒。<br>如果飞机坠毁，飞行员也会丧命。但别忘了，轰炸机上有工程师。发挥想象力，使用手头的资源解决遇到的问题。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/484ac18fd8ae52833afb99eb661ec6af.poster.avif?t=1767865416\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/484ac18fd8ae52833afb99eb661ec6af.webm?t=1767865416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>管理飞机</strong><br>你的任务不仅是对付地对空导弹以及梅塞施密特中队。<br>你还需要监控燃油、弹药以及炸弹。<br>在高空飞行时，你还要监控氧气供给，确保队员都戴上了氧气面罩。<br>有时，你需要扔掉部分货物，才能靠有限燃油成功抵达机场。<br>此外，你还要应付发动机起火、机轮受损、炸弹舱门卡死等技术故障。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/380e2c63f1f0310a7fc2baffcb9bb2d6.poster.avif?t=1767865416\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/380e2c63f1f0310a7fc2baffcb9bb2d6.webm?t=1767865416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>非头等舱</strong><br>驾驭空中堡垒可不是搭乘头等舱班机。船员将在艰苦的环境下面对巨大压力，在枪林弹雨中求生。<br>使用武器对付地对空导弹以及敌人的战斗机。<br><br>布下复杂的阵型，增加中队的防御力。12架飞机将成为坚不可摧的空中堡垒。你可以管理整个中队来完成任务。<br><br>机长，祝你好运！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/29eeb9c1f60c570ce16d6f91db15fc92.poster.avif?t=1767865416\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1502460/extras/29eeb9c1f60c570ce16d6f91db15fc92.webm?t=1767865416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
